{
  "stem": "15694.12",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, during the six weeks still in the camp, I got myself an outfit-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] short trousers; a shirt, which I didn't know whether it was gray or brown or both, no buttons; and a green straw hat; no socks, but ankle-high boots.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Surely a very funny outfit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it's how I walked-- in Italy, walked into a rather posh cafe, people sitting outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're looking at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how could I explain to them that I am richer than they are?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their amused glances did not hurt me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They amused me as well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we were taken to a camp in Modena.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was also the trickery I mentioned to get more than my ration, you know, and borrowing other people's ration cards and showing them in a way that they couldn't see that they were stamped already.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's, you know, it's conjuring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe you may call it not nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- my spirits to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--get-- survive, carried on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I must say this, that when in six months in Italy-- oh, I didn't go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many, many, many years later I went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, it was by then Israel, and for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and, well, I gained-- in six months, I gained about a hundred weight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I was liberated, I weighed half-- about half my weight or less, around 30 or 32 kilograms, which was less than half my weight.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every doctor will tell you that nobody can go back to less your half weight and live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so this is, more or less, where I think I will end my story because what comes now goes into my second book.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And was it worse to survive?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
